.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-9::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, aristoff
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Beverage   | 7up         | coffee    |
| Food       | spinach     | cucumber  |
| Hobby      | board-games | chess     |
| Cigar        | aristoff     | havana |

